150	\subsection{Forget-and-recover: bridging $k$-module and abelian-group values}
151	
152	\begin{definition}\leanok
153	[Forget-and-recover natural iso for the $k$-module structure sheaf]
154	  \label{def:Scheme_toModuleKSheaf_forgetCompare}
